I"Ì<p>The earliest accessible English version is that of <a href="/authors/jacobi_j">Jacobi</a>, 1725, printed in the 1754 <em>Moravian Hymn Book.</em> The translations by this author are usually very crude and painfully laborious, but in the present case, with a few notable exceptions, he has very well caught the ring and spirit of Gerhardt. Later compilers and publishers of hymns would of course omit the lines:</p>

